---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Privacy Policy - AyurCure Daily"
    description="Understand how AyurCure Daily collects, uses, and protects your data in accordance with our privacy practices."
>
    <Header />

    <main class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                    Privacy Policy
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Your privacy is important to us. Here's how we handle your
                    data at AyurCure Daily.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 space-y-8 text-gray-700"
            >
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                        1. Information We Collect
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        We may collect basic personal information such as your
                        name, email address, and browsing behavior when you
                        visit our website or subscribe to our newsletter.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                        2. How We Use Your Information
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Your data is used solely to improve your experience with
                        AyurCure Daily, including:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
                        <li>Sending you health tips and updates</li>
                        <li>Personalizing your experience</li>
                        <li>Improving site functionality and content</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                        3. Data Sharing & Security
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        We do not sell or share your personal information with
                        third parties. All data is stored securely and access is
                        limited to authorized personnel only.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Cookies</h2>
                    <p>
                        AyurCure Daily uses cookies to enhance your browsing
                        experience. You can choose to disable cookies through
                        your browser settings.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>
                        You have the right to request access to or deletion of
                        your data at any time. To make such requests, please
                        contact us at <a
                            href="mailto:ayurcuredaily@gmail.com"
                            class="text-primary-600 underline"
                            >ayurcuredaily@gmail.com</a
                        >.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                        6. Policy Updates
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        We may update our privacy policy occasionally. Any
                        changes will be posted on this page with a revised date.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>
                        If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy
                        Policy, feel free to contact us at <a
                            href="mailto:ayurcuredaily@gmail.com"
                            class="text-primary-600 underline"
                            >ayurcuredaily@gmail.com</a
                        >.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
